Good work. You're the student from the academy who came for
the report, right? When you're ready, please let me know.
Are you going to the 'Cordin Underground Sewer'?!

Good work. You're the student from the academy who came for
the report, right? When you're ready, please let me know.
Are you going to the underground sewer?

This is the soldiers' dormitory. It's off-limits to anyone
who is not authorized.

\SE[2] Beyond here is outside the castle... I don't have
permission to leave.

This is Cordin Castle up ahead. You can enter the courtyard,
but please refrain from excessive sightseeing.

My husband was attacked by a monster in the basement while
he was at work. Fortunately, he only got minor injuries...
Will you all be able to defeat it? Please do your best for
the sake of our household finances...!

I'm trying to attract customers... hehe ♥ Oh my, I
accidentally seduced a girl.

...Oh, you there. Did you just give me a quick that kind of
look? Well, that's not a problem. Hehe ♥
スライドスピード = def

My colleague was complaining about being sent on a frontier
inspection. They were saying something about a Hajikko
Village. I wonder what they're going to do in such a rural
place...

Since Koudain became the current king, things have become
prosperous. I don't mean to speak ill of the previous king,
but... the current king is like, Bam! and decides
everything, so he's really cool.

When the current administration took over, the king
eliminated all the corrupt parts of the government in one
fell swoop, pushing aside all opposition from the
bureaucrats clinging to their existing interests.

That was exhilarating. It felt like witnessing a small
revolution.

C-Could it be... that Lunaroa...!? I-I'm... a fan!! I've
admired you for so long...!!!

Eh... You're Vega from Flame Swift...!? No way...!! Oh
my...!! I need to dress up...!!

\SE[90] Eh... What...? Flame Swift...? I've never heard of
it before.

I also want to enter the academy in the future and become a
wizard! Then I'll volunteer as a soldier and become a magic
swordsman!

\SE[7]That's a good plan for the future. I'll be cheering
for you.
\SE[2] (I wonder if he actually likes children...)

Lulu~lululu~. \.Let's beat up those bad guys in the Yuri
scene~.

This is something that's popular among kids right now. Will
you big sisters sing along too?

Hmm... I volunteered to be a soldier, but I was rejected. It
seems like the requirements are high because there is also a
magic academy...
Well... let's go and inform the soldiers at the scene first.

If you need any item replenishment, please let me know. Even
though we call ourselves a team, it's still the two of you
who are the core. I want to leave the decision-making in
that regard up to you.
\SM[nod]\SE[2] I understand. Leave it to me.

Well, shall we go? We can't keep the two of them waiting for
too long, after all.

\SE[3] (I suddenly ended up being alone with them... What
should I do... I'm actually quite shy around people...)

It's mandatory to have security guards stationed at the
weapon shop. It's a recently enacted law.
Hey, let's play that Lunaroa game! Let's gooo...!

Zubyaaan!! Bashuu!! Dogogogoon!! Shugoon!! Doon!!
Guchaguchaa!! Zugobaan!!
Gee! I got hit! Zugogoban! Bajudon! Gushagusha! Guchoo!
